ConfigLampTimes is a mod for Factorio.

It allows to configure the start and end brightness levels for lamp staggering.

To be used with pure vanilla or mods that add or change lamps.
All lamps share the same staggering parameters.

To disable staggering use the same value for staggering start and end brightness.


Licensed under the GNU GPL-3.0 or later.


History:

- Version 0.0.0 is the first version and compatible to Factorio 0.16 with bugfix-level 23 or greater
